OL,5,G1400 Martin Clunes: Islands of America
OL,6,     FStarting at Washington's San Juan
OL,7,     FIslands, Martin heads to
OL,8,     FCalifornia's Channel Islands. He
OL,9,     Fcrosses 2,000 miles to Avery
OL,10,     FIsland, witnessing Louisiana's
OL,11,     Fdisappearing coastal communities.
OL,12,G1500 Martin Clunes: Islands of America
OL,13,     FMartin visits Puerto Rico,
OL,14,     Frecovering from Hurricane Maria's
OL,15,     Fdevastation. He explores Georgia
OL,16,     Fand Carolina's Sea Islands, home
OL,17,     Fto the Gullah Geechee people
OL,18,     Fpreserving African heritage.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
